claim.claim-text:
1. A composition comprising 
(i) an aviation fuel; and 
(ii) a deposit inhibiting compound of the formula I 
P-Q-R   (I) 
in which P is a polymeric hydrocarbyl group 
in which Q is an optional ring system; 
in which R is a group selected from H and hydrocarbyl; 
wherein if R is a hydrocarbyl group it is free of a carboxylic acid group (—COOH); 
wherein Q together with R contains no greater than 2 nitrogens; and 
wherein when Q together with R contains 2 nitrogens each of the nitrogens is a member of a heterocyclic ring.
